  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201305/c73a3ff60ad94e1ba13db818ca31c2c5.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/11921/\" target=\"_blank\">《标准美音模仿秀》</a>是一档沪江部落的原创口语互动节目（<a href=\"http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/11921/item/766124/\" target=\"_blank\">戳我去参加节目&gt;&gt;</a>），主持人截取30秒左右的英语音频，然后对音频进行重点讲解和示范模仿，并对大家递交的口语模仿作品进行一对一的点评，想要练习纯正美音的童鞋赶快行动起来吧！<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/11921/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/d5e293c817a6488d819f0c13a95230e1.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\" /></a>去沪江部落订阅本节目！</p>\n<p>\n\t今日主持人：<strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">jamesryan457</span></strong></p>\n<p>\n\t20秒音频：<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p581328\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\t小编模仿音频：<strong>&nbsp;</strong><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p581328\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\t模仿文本： During the 18 months The Band Perry spent working on &quot;<a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/Pioneer\" target=\"_blank\">Pioneer</a>,&quot; Kimberly and her younger brothers Reid and Neil faced some challenges. Kimberly says, we had so many questions about our future, both personally and professionally. We also had to let go of fear and trust the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/boldness\" target=\"_blank\">boldness</a> that has always informed our creative decisions. Kimberly and Neil explained what &quot;Pioneer&quot; means to them.在佩里乐队制作Pioneer的8个月中，金伯利和她的两个弟弟里德和尼尔面对着很多挑战。金伯利说：&ldquo;从个人和专业的角度，我们都对未来有很多疑问。但是我们不得不放下恐惧，并相信一直赋予我们创造性决断的魄力。&rdquo;金伯利和内尔解释了对他们而言Pioneer的含义。 <span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"></span></p>\n<p>\n\t重点单词发音讲解：<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p581328\" tit